this, I'm also thinking that some part of Nestle are also shaped to be

00:18:16.839 --> 00:18:19.839
like I would say startup like or have this freedom.

00:18:19.839 --> 00:18:22.839
So there is still even though there is it's a big company result of the process

00:18:22.839 --> 00:18:26.839
and everything, which is giving also a certain security and coherence.

00:18:27.839 --> 00:18:32.839
Then there is also this innovation and entrepreneurship that is visible

00:18:32.839 --> 00:18:34.839
into some areas of the company.

