your role as head of technology and now a data scientist?

00:18:43.839 --> 00:18:46.839
I'm doing more hands on things as a data scientist.

00:18:46.839 --> 00:18:47.839
That was one of the goal.

00:18:48.839 --> 00:18:52.839
You know, when you are head of technology, it's the activity was a lot

00:18:52.839 --> 00:18:59.839
around supervising people, not supervising in terms of people management,

