And then you will see these are the types of times of, you know,

00:19:41.839 --> 00:19:47.839
the head of technology, the experts coming in and then firsthand say

00:19:47.839 --> 00:19:48.839
whether it's possible or not.

00:19:50.839 --> 00:19:54.839
And in that regard, I'm not doing this anymore at all as a data scientist

