in this way because I'm involved in the project, I would say,

00:19:59.839 --> 00:20:00.839
really much more hands on.

00:20:01.839 --> 00:20:08.839
And I might then that there is no interaction with, I would say,

00:20:08.839 --> 00:20:10.839
customer who would have a specific project.

00:20:10.839 --> 00:20:14.839
It would be more internal customers and internal project that are being

00:20:14.839 --> 00:20:16.839
shaped and developed.

00:20:17.839 --> 00:20:25.839
So, yeah, so there is this hands on thing and I could be much more focused

00:20:25.839 --> 00:20:30.839
on data science activity itself and develop also in that field that is

00:20:30.839 --> 00:20:37.839
also taking off a lot with now more recently also on larger data sets

00:20:37.839 --> 00:20:38.839
as well.

