Sorry if I mispronounced that.

00:20:45.839 --> 00:20:48.839
But Niels, I'll give you a second if you want to ask that yourself.

00:20:48.839 --> 00:20:49.839
Otherwise, I can ask it.

00:20:50.839 --> 00:20:51.839
Yeah, sure.

00:20:51.839 --> 00:20:52.839
Can you hear me?

00:20:52.839 --> 00:20:53.839
Loud and clear.

